query_login_mode
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_login_mode

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_login_mode -  This method returns our login restriction level.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_login_mode()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0, 1 or 2
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/login_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns our login restriction level.
The return value is one of the following.
0 - unrestricted
1 - restricted to playtesters
2 - restricted to creators
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_login_mode()

.EP

